{
  "text": "For example, the majority of ASFV outbreaks and spread within the DP populations in endemic settings, such as Northern Uganda, are most likely related to factors associated with human management practices and behavior in the DP value chain -and not to the presence of WP [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, in the edge of protected areas, WP may play an important role for the persistence of ASFV and other diseases in the environment or for their introduction into naive populations of DPs.",
  "correct_citation": {
